data.description:
Nestled in the serene The Woodlands Hills subdivision of Willis, Tx, this 2-story home presents an ideal blend of comfort and modern living. With 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 1 half bathroom, this residence spans approx 2,921 sq ft of thoughtfully designed space. Inside, a spacious living room and dining room on the 1st floor create a welcoming ambiance, complemented by the functional kitchen layout that boasts a breakfast bar, island (w/out cooktop), ample cabinetry for storage and an office/spare that is available for multi-purpose use. The primary bedroom, complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring a shower, is situated on the 2nd floor along with additional bedrooms that provide versatile living options. The 2nd-floor game room offers an expansive area for entertainment and relaxation. Additional features include a fenced backyard, 2 car-garage, and a gaslog fireplace! Property is located in the Wills ISD, including easy access to TX-75 & FM 830. Schedule your showing today!

Data provided by HAR.com 2023 - All information provided should be independently verified.
